players.name: Elvis Chipezeze
players.summary: Elvis Chipezeze is a Zimbabwean football player. He plays in South Africa for Magesi.

players.name: Martin Mapisa
players.summary: Martin Mapisa is a Zimbabwean football player wo plays as a goalkeeper. He plays for Spanish club Málaga City.

players.name: Washington Arubi
players.summary: Washington Arubi is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Premier Soccer League side Marumo Gallants.

players.name: Gerald Takwara
players.summary: John Gerald Tungamirai Takwara is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as a centre back for Iraq Stars League club Al-Minaa and the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Sean Fusire
players.summary: Sean Sheunesu Fusire is a professional footballer who plays as a right-back for EFL Championship club Sheffield Wednesday. Born in England, he plays international football for Zimbabwe.

players.name: Munashe Garananga
players.summary: Munashe Peter Garananga is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as a centre-back for Danish Superliga club Copenhagen and the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Divine Lunga
players.summary: Divine Lunga was born in Bulawayo on 28 May 1995 is a Zimbabwean footballer who plays as a defender for Mamelodi Sundowns and the Zimbabwe national football team.

players.name: Brendan Galloway
players.summary: Brendan Joel Zibusiso Galloway is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as a defender for EFL League One club Plymouth Argyle. A former youth international for England, Galloway represents the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Teenage Hadebe
players.summary: Teenage Lingani Hadebe is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as a defender for Major League Soccer club FC Cincinnati. He also plays for the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Godknows Murwira
players.summary: Godknows Murwira is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as a right-back for Zimbabwe Premier Soccer League club Scottland and the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Alec Mudimu
players.summary: Alec Mudimu is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Flint Town United and the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Prosper Padera
players.summary: Prosper Padera is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as defensive midfielder for Veikkausliiga club SJK Seinäjoki and the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Jonah Fabisch
players.summary: Jonah Reinhard Fabisch is a professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for 3. Liga club Erzgebirge Aue. Born in Kenya, he plays for the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Andy Rinomhota
players.summary: Andrew Farai Rinomhota is a professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for EFL League One club Reading. Born in England, he plays for the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Knowledge Musona
players.summary: Knowledge Musona is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as a left winger or forward for Scottland. Musona, also captained the Zimbabwe national team prior to retiring from international football. Previously, he has played senior football in South Africa, Belgium and Germany.

players.name: Marvelous Nakamba
players.summary: Marvelous Nakamba is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as a defensive midfielder for EFL League One club Luton Town and the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Tawanda Chirewa
players.summary: Tawanda Blessing Chirewa is a professional footballer who plays as a right winger for Premier League club Wolverhampton Wanderers. Born in England, he represents Zimbabwe internationally.

players.name: Prince Dube
players.summary: Prince Mpumelelo Dube is a Zimbabwean professional footballer, who most recently played forward for Tanzanian Premier League club Young Africans Sports Club and the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Macauley Bonne
players.summary: Macauley Miles Bonne is a professional footballer who plays as a striker for Isthmian League North side Maldon & Tiptree. Born in England, he plays for the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Bill Antonio
players.summary: Bill Leeroy Antonio is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as a winger for Belgian club Mechelen, and the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Daniel Msendami
players.summary: Daniel Msendami is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as a winger for South African Premiership club Marumo Gallants and the Zimbabwe national team.

players.name: Tawanda Maswanhise
players.summary: Tawanda Jethro Maswanhise is a Zimbabwean footballer who plays as a midfielder or winger for Scottish Premiership club Motherwell and the Zimbabwe national football team.

players.name: Ishmael Wadi
players.summary: Ishmael Wadi is a Zimbabwean professional footballer who plays as a forward for JDR Stars and the Zimbabwe national team. He was named in Zimbabwe's squad for the 2021 Africa Cup of Nations.
